Name: SUB FOUR -the uncle-

After about 3:58:00-3:59:00, the Final Spurt mode will begin. After the Final Spurt, your time will be shown. Good Ending: become 'SUB FOUR' Game Over #1: couldn't become 'SUB FOUR' Game Over #2: retired Cheat Ending: cheated
